<text top="661" left="90" width="69" height="19" font="6"><b>Agenda</b></text>
<text top="703" left="122" width="381" height="14" font="1">The situation in Tajikistan and along the Tajik-Afghan border</text>
<text top="739" left="153" width="514" height="14" font="1">Progress report of the Secretary-General on the situation in Tajikistan (S/1998/113)</text>
